Package: testhta
Title: Validate Cost-Effectiveness and Decision-Analytic Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nathan", "Green", email = "n.green@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides a validation framework for applying software engineering 
    best practices, specifically unit testing, to health economic and health 
    technology assessment (HTA) models. By leveraging the 'testthat' package, 
    it helps modelers verify that cohort Markov models behave as expected 
    under specific mathematical and economic conditions (e.g. discounting, 
    life expectancy limits, and extreme parameter values).
